{%- comment -%}
  The feature-badge glyphs, exported from Figma.

  A snippet because the badge row is painted on EVERY line-item card, but a block may
  emit `content_for 'blocks'` only once — so the first card renders the real badge
  blocks (editable, carrying shopify_attributes) and the rest render an identical
  attribute-free copy built from block.blocks. Both paths draw from here, so the
  artwork exists once.

  Accepts: icon — 'wind' | 'care' | 'organic'
{%- endcomment -%}
